,{"s":46.96,"e":50.02,"text":"Pulled the gold out the vault, put a promise in the sky"},{"s":50.02,"e":53.24,"text":"Called it currency but the current carry every man dry"},{"s":53.24,"e":59.68,"text":"Federal reserve, neither federal nor reserve Private printing press, public catching every"},{"s":59.68,"e":62.54,"text":"curve Nineteen thirteen, the snake crawled into"},{"s":62.54,"e":65.78,"text":"the law Took the people's purse and replaced it with"},{"s":65.78,"e":68.96,"text":"the mall Inflation eat the wage like a locust eat"},{"s":68.96,"e":72.56,"text":"a field Pension turn to dust for the worker get the"},{"s":72.56,"e":75,"text":"will Six-five Davis standing where the prophets"},{"s":75,"e":78.66,"text":"had to kneel Stone in the pocket and the pocket made of"},{"s":78.66,"e":82.3,"text":"steel The lion got a forehead, kid got a stone"},{"s":82.3,"e":88.22,"text":"The lion got a balance sheet, kid got a home The lion got the printing press, kid got the"},{"s":88.22,"e":91.64,"text":"truth The lion got the centuries, kid got the youth"},{"s":91.7,"e":94.82,"text":"Six-five Davis Slinging the hand"},{"s":95.2,"e":101.14,"text":"Pyramid falling on the promised land Capstone tumble, eye on the floor"},{"s":101.28,"e":105.92,"text":"Holy ghost knocking at the central bank door Six-five Davis"},{"s":105.92,"e":109.12,"text":"Taller than the lion Bigger than the giant"},{"s":109.12,"e":113.8,"text":"Smaller than the sky One stone, one shot, one breath, one song"},{"s":113.8,"e":117.12,"text":"Federal reserve falling Kid stay calm"},{"s":117.12,"e":120.08,"text":"They watermark the dollar with the eye that never blinks"},{"s":120.5,"e":123.26,"text":"Pyramid unfinished, that's the part nobody thinks"},{"s":123.66,"e":126.44,"text":"Cornerstone rejected by the builders of the bank"},{"s":126.44,"e":129.58,"text":"Kid pick it up, put it in a sling, let it clank"},{"s":129.64,"e":136.02,"text":"Truth is the stone, voice is the velocity Code is the leather, faith is the ferocity"},{"s":136.02,"e":142.4,"text":"Sling world twice, three times for the trinity Aim for the forehead of the soulless infinity"},{"s":142.4,"e":148.82,"text":"Goliath laughing, armor weigh a thousand tons Kid travel like some stone to lungs"},{"s":148.82,"e":155.04,"text":"Five smooth pebbles picked from the brook One for the giant, four for whoever else shook"},{"s":155.04,"e":158.28,"text":"They grinning, they grinning But the kingdom ain't for sale"},{"s":158.3,"e":161.52,"text":"They grinning, they grinning But the breath behind the kid don't fail"},{"s":161.52,"e":164.74,"text":"They grinning, they grinning Pyramid teetering, capstone fall"},{"s":164.74,"e":172.36,"text":"They grinning, they grinning Six, five, Davis standing tall"},{"s":172.52,"e":174.46,"text":"Drum kicks back and boom"},{"s":187.24,"e":193.08,"text":"Pyramid crack, concrete dust on the marble Eye on the bill, blink twice, then it start to gobble"},{"s":193.7,"e":199.86,"text":"Greenback faded, value never was the paper Value was the labor of the hands, the giant tapered"},{"s":199.86,"e":202.6,"text":"Kid step over rubble where the temple used to loom"},{"s":202.6,"e":205.8,"text":"Plant a garden in the crater, watch the cornflowers bloom"},{"s":205.8,"e":212.16,"text":"Into new currency, trust, sweat neighbor Back by the maker, now by some paid persuader"},{"s":212.5,"e":218.6,"text":"Six, five, David ain't a king, ain't a tyrant Just a kid with a stone telling giants to stop lying"},{"s":218.6,"e":225.26,"text":"Walk the people home, leave the pyramid in pieces Federal reserve dissolved and the burden finally ceases"},{"s":225.26,"e":231.68,"text":"Six, five, David slinging the hand Pyramid falling on the promised land"},{"s":231.78,"e":237.86,"text":"Capstone tumble, eye on the floor Holy ghost knocking at the central bank door"},{"s":237.86,"e":244.26,"text":"Six, five, David taller than the lion Bigger than the giant, smaller than the sky"},{"s":244.26,"e":250.62,"text":"One stone, one shot, one breath, one song Federal reserve falling, kids stay calm"},{"s":250.62,"e":257.14,"text":"When the lord set the stone, the builders refused Become the cornerstone, the kingdom in use"},{"s":257.14,"e":265.7,"text":"Six, five, David walking off the field Swinging the pocket, kid done used"}],"duration":282.5199890136719,"source":"whisper","generatedAt":"2026-05-22T02:29:18.357Z","model":"whisper-1"}